:"2019-09-12T11:02:37.000Z","msg":"同佢講<br />\n見到跳閘可以同狗鐵職員講<br />\n掂你係非禮+普通襲擊<br />\n唔比你走係非法禁固<br />\n唔放手就開佢拖，跟住走，唔好同佢糾纏<br />\n記住<br />\n跳閘係唔關狗事<br />\n有狗埋黎第一時間拎張id出黎問佢洗唔撚洗查/搜身<br />\n咁做係先手令佢冇機會用懷疑你係ii/通輯犯之類原因留難你<br />\n之後就重覆第一點，覺得有人遺反狗鐵附例可以同職員講，問佢而家係秘撈定濫用納稅人既錢幫狗鐵做野<br />\n跟手直接走<br />\n同樣，如故意阻攔係犯法<br />\n最緊要大聲，惡<br />\n惡過佢佢就唔敢亂黎"},{"pid":"9b46403bfcd4179d16eff7decd7ce27a84bd12a8","tid":1563311,"uid":303464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:11:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e6f31573410536775bde7ad3e5d860ccb50aa2d","tid":1563311,"uid":303464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:42:47.000Z","msg":"多謝果幾位發聲嘅好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一世平安"},{"pid":"1c6f4a633a3b478e4689afee578dc169d774e265","tid":1563311,"uid":276749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:44:23.000Z","msg":"今晚仲有冇人唱歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95395c3541d62cf85a24db100a2ee1c04b9344a7","tid":1563311,"uid":268928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:39:28.000Z","msg":"係咪好撚肥個個"},{"pid":"db6da6af0478b704aae9aecd0b7b7a733e038b70","tid":1563311,"uid":303464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95395c3541d62cf85a24db100a2ee1c04b9344a7","tid":1563311,"uid":268928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:39:28.000Z","msg":"係咪好撚肥個個"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:46:11.000Z","msg":"係啊   慣犯黎？？"},{"pid":"18c780f4d3bca3326862c0c5fd5e1a7d08e0580e","tid":1563311,"uid":268928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db6da6af0478b704aae9aecd0b7b7a733e038b70","tid":1563311,"uid":303464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95395c3541d62cf85a24db100a2ee1c04b9344a7","tid":1563311,"uid":268928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:39:28.000Z","msg":"係咪好撚肥個個"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:46:11.000Z","msg":"係啊   慣犯黎？？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:49:45.000Z","msg":"唔知 不過好似得把口 唔會追上去"},{"pid":"7598aea6a448242c4e4b2b1090df9cfd20a27907","tid":1563311,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T02:03:11.000Z","msg":"和理非式搭鐵三寶：<br />\n1.正常八達通<br />\n2.綠卡<br />\n3.隨身已入閘單程飛一張（最平一個站既飛就得）<br />\n<br />\n出入當然用綠卡，如果遇到food panda查飛，因為佢地手上多數得八達通查飛機<br />\n<br />\n情境一：<br />\n已入閘時查飛，show 單程飛<br />\n<br />\n情境二：<br />\n出閘後查飛，show正常八達通<br />\n<br />\n情境三：<br />\n查到無效飛，無賴扮唔知/補飛/罰錢/9秒9"}]}